dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile contain statistics on household building materials from the 2010 Panama Population and Housing Census. The census information was collected by the Instituto Nacional de Estadistica y Censo in Panama in Panama on May 16, 2010. The original questionnaire and other supporting documentation for this census is included with this download. These data are intended for researchers, students, and policy makers for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production.
dc_creator_sm: Panama. Dirección de Estadística y Censo
